Binary/source change: animation timer CallLater fix
===================================================

Purpose
-------
Replace the first animated GIF repaint loop, which used wx.Timer event binding,
with a one-shot wx.CallLater loop. GIF frames decoded correctly, but the timer
path did not advance the visible image in live testing.

Changed file
------------
library.zip

